  <title>Qualist Account Update</title>
  <style>
    {{{css}}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Qualist Account Update!</h1>
    <p id="user_name">Dear, <strong>{{name}}</strong></p>
    <p>We hope this email finds you well.</p>
    <p>We're writing to inform you that your account information on Qualist has been updated by your administrator.</p>
    <p>Below are your updated login credentials:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
      <li><strong>Password:</strong> [Your password remains unchanged]</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We recommend that you log in and review your account details to ensure everything is accurate. If you have any concerns or questions regarding these changes, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    <p>Remember to always choose a strong and secure password for your account to maintain the integrity of your data.</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a valued member of Qualist. We appreciate your cooperation and understanding.</p>
    <p>Best Regards,<br>The Qualist Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
